  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Some of these people would have either several functions or have trade or businesses besides.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "For instance, the beadle of, of the shul, a certain Mr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Hirsch, who at one time was a broom maker.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had a factory for making brooms.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The factory, of course, consisted of himself, his children, with a few pieces of equipment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they made all the brooms for the whole town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "At another time-- I think it was the same Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Hirsch or somebody else, for instance-- had a, a, a dairy plant.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I don't even know whether or not it can be dignified with the term plant.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But again, there were a few pieces of equipment which are used to separate milk and make butter and, and sour milk and things of that kind.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then, you know, you would go down the street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And even, for instance, what moving there was-- of course, moving was done by a big cart with some of these heavy horses that you occasionally see on old beer ads.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That was also Jewishly-owned-- and although the owner may have been a, a Jewishly-unlettered, he was an Orthodox or a member of an Orthodox community.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "There hardware store, the letter store-- there, there were tradesmen who, certainly in the eye of the more Hasidic and Talmudically better-trained Jews would look down on the [YIDDISH SPEECH], the, the plain folk, nonetheless were, were members of a, of an Orthodox Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And, you know, observed the rituals and the holidays and sometimes were quite self-possessed members of, of the synagogues and, and various institutions.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You could actually say that there was hardly any profession or any trade in which Jews did not participate and which were not a part of this closed economy.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
